<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''苯丙酮尿症'''，又稱'''苯酮尿症'''（{{lang-en|Phenylketonuria}}，縮寫為'''PKU'''），是一種[[遺傳性代謝缺陷|遺傳性代謝缺陷]]，肇因於[[苯丙氨酸|苯丙氨酸]]這種[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]的代謝能力下降<ref name="Al2015">{{cite journal | vauthors = Al Hafid N, Christodoulou J | title = Phenylketonuria: a review of current and future treatments | journal = Translational Pediatrics | volume = 4 | issue = 4 | pages = 304–17 | date = October 2015 | pmid = 26835392 | pmc = 4728993 | doi = 10.3978/j.issn.2224-4336.2015.10.07 }}</ref>。如果不接受治療，苯丙酮尿症可能引起[[智能障礙|智能障礙]]、[[癲癇發作|癲癇發作]]、帶來行為問題以及[[精神疾患|精神疾患]]；患者可能也會帶有發霉氣味跟較淺的膚色<ref name=NIH2016>{{cite web|title=phenylketonuria|url=https://ghr.nlm.nih.gov/condition/phenylketonuria|website=Genetics Home Reference|accessdate=12 September 2016|date=September 8, 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160727233812/https://ghr.nlm.nih.gov/condition/phenylketonuria|archivedate=2016-07-27}}</ref>。如果產婦患者沒有好好接受治療，可能會帶給婴儿心臟疾病、[[小頭畸形|小頭畸形]]，或導致婴儿[[低出生體重兒|出生體重過低]]<ref name=NIH2016/>。

<!-- Cause, mechanism, and diagnosis -->
苯丙酮尿症係為一種[[遺傳疾病|遺傳疾病]][[遺傳|承襲]]自父母<ref name=NIH2016/>，由於[[苯丙氨酸羥化酶|苯丙氨酸羥化酶]]（簡稱為 PAH）基因變異使得[[酶|酶]]的產量低下<ref name=NIH2016/>，導致飲食中攝取的苯丙胺酸堆積，達到可能會中毒的濃度<ref name=NIH2016/>。此症為[[隱性|隱性]]遺傳，意即必然是患者父母雙方的基因複製皆發生變異，才會導致患者罹患此症<ref name=NIH2016/>。苯丙酮尿症有兩種型態，典型 PKU 跟變型 PKU，差異在於酶是否功能正常<ref name=NIH2016/>。僅從父母之一遺傳到變異基因複製者通常不會有症狀<ref name=NIH2016/>。有許多國家提供{{le|新生兒篩檢|newborn screening programs}}以過濾出此症<ref name=Al2015/>。

<!-- Cause, mechanism, and diagnosis -->
治療方式為採用低苯丙氨酸的飲食及特殊補充劑<ref name=NIH2013Tx>{{cite web|title=What are common treatments for phenylketonuria (PKU)?|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pku/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|website=NICHD|accessdate=12 September 2016|date=2013-08-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005121620/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pku/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|archivedate=5 October 2016}}</ref>，必須給嬰兒患者服用特殊[[配方奶粉|配方奶粉]]佐以少量[[母乳|母乳]]<ref name=NIH2013Tx/>。在嬰兒誕生後，必須盡快讓其開始低苯丙氨酸的飲食，如果不能終生維持，至少需持續十年<ref name=NIH2013Tx/><ref name=Eng2013>{{cite web|title=Clinical Commissioning Policy: Sapropterin (Kuvan®) For Phenylketonuria: Use in Pregnancy|url=https://www.england.nhs.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/e12-p-a.pdf|accessdate=25 March 2018|page=4|date=April 2013|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308012423/https://www.england.nhs.uk/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/e12-p-a.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。如果嚴格執行飲食限制，早期診斷出此症的患者仍可以跟常人一般健康，[[壽命|壽命]]與常人無異<ref name=NIH2000>{{cite web|title=National Institutes of Health Consensus Development Conference Statement Phenylketonuria: Screening and Management|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/publications/pubs/pku/pages/sub3.aspx|website=NICHD|accessdate=12 September 2016|date=October 16–18, 2000|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005002837/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/publications/pubs/pku/pages/sub3.aspx|archivedate=5 October 2016}}</ref>。療效需依定期接受[[血液檢查|血液檢查]]來監測<ref name=NIH2000/。使用[[四氫生物蝶呤|四氫生物蝶呤]]藥物或許對部分患者有效<ref name=NIH2013Tx/>。患者需要避免某些生活中常见的食品添加剂，比如，患者需要避免摄入阿斯巴甜<ref>{{Cite web|title=Phenylketonuria: MedlinePlus Medical Encyclopedia|url=https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/001166.htm|accessdate=2019-12-20|work=medlineplus.gov|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318150503/https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/001166.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Treatment and prognosis-->
在1.2萬新生兒中約有1人會罹患苯丙酮尿症<ref name=Bern2015>{{cite book|last1=Bernstein|first1=Laurie E.|last2=Rohr|first2=Fran|last3=Helm|first3=Joanna R.|title=Nutrition Management of Inherited Metabolic Diseases: Lessons from Metabolic University|date=2015|publisher=Springer|isbn=9783319146218|page=91|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=q1LMCQAAQBAJ&pg=PA91 | deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911010922/https://books.google.ca/books?id=q1LMCQAAQBAJ&pg=PA91|archive-date=2017-09-11}}</ref>，男性和女性的患病機率一致<ref>{{cite book|last1=Marcdante|first1=Karen|last2=Kliegman|first2=Robert M.|title=Nelson Essentials of Pediatrics|date=2014|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9780323226981|page=150|edition=7|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=hsY0AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA150 | deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911010922/https://books.google.ca/books?id=hsY0AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA150|archive-date=2017-09-11}}</ref>。1934 年，[[挪威|挪威]][[醫生|醫生]]{{le|Ivar Asbjørn Følling}}發現此症，1953 年，發現此症受飲食影響甚鉅<ref name=Kal2010>{{cite book|last1=Kalter|first1=Harold | name-list-format = vanc |title=Teratology in the Twentieth Century Plus Ten|date=2010|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=9789048188208|pages=89–92|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=DykKlVU0V-oC&pg=PA89 |deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911010922/https://books.google.ca/books?id=DykKlVU0V-oC&pg=PA89|archive-date=2017-09-11}}</ref>。2014 年提出的[[基因治療|基因治療]]雖受到期待，但仍有賴大量的學術研究支持<ref name=Camp2014>{{cite journal | vauthors = Camp KM, Parisi MA, Acosta PB, Berry GT, Bilder DA, Blau N, Bodamer OA, Brosco JP, Brown CS, Burlina AB, Burton BK, Chang CS, Coates PM, Cunningham AC, Dobrowolski SF, Ferguson JH, Franklin TD, Frazier DM, Grange DK, Greene CL, Groft SC, Harding CO, Howell RR, Huntington KL, Hyatt-Knorr HD, Jevaji IP, Levy HL, Lichter-Konecki U, Lindegren ML, Lloyd-Puryear MA, Matalon K, MacDonald A, McPheeters ML, Mitchell JJ, Mofidi S, Moseley KD, Mueller CM, Mulberg AE, Nerurkar LS, Ogata BN, Pariser AR, Prasad S, Pridjian G, Rasmussen SA, Reddy UM, Rohr FJ, Singh RH, Sirrs SM, Stremer SE, Tagle DA, Thompson SM, Urv TK, Utz JR, van Spronsen F, Vockley J, Waisbren SE, Weglicki LS, White DA, Whitley CB, Wilfond BS, Yannicelli S, Young JM | display-authors = 6 | title = Phenylketonuria Scientific Review Conference: state of the science and future research needs | journal = Molecular Genetics and Metabolism | volume = 112 | issue = 2 | pages = 87–122 | date = June 2014 | pmid = 24667081 | doi = 10.1016/j.ymgme.2014.02.013 }}</ref>。

== 苯丙酮尿症發現 ==

1934年挪威的佛寧（Folling）醫師在家族性智障病患的尿液中發現有特殊陳腐物味道，後來才知道該物質是苯丙酮酸 （Phenylpyruvic Acid），在1937年正式命名為苯酮尿症（Phenylketonuria；PKU）。苯酮尿症是一種體染色體隱性遺傳疾病，主要是由於體內苯丙胺酸 （Phenylalanine；Phe）羥化（Hydroxylation）成酪胺酸（Tyrosine；Tyr）的代謝途徑機能障礙所引起的先天代謝異常疾病。目前已知有五種不同的酶缺陷會造成此種代謝機能障礙；這些酶包括有苯丙胺酸羥化酶（Phenylalanine Hydroxylase；PAH）、鳥嘌呤核苷三磷酸環化水解酶Ⅰ（GTP CyclohydrolaseⅠ；GTPCHⅠ）、丙二酮四氫喋呤合成酶（6-pyruvoyl Tetrahydropterin Synthase；PTPS）、雙氫喋啶還原酶（Dihydropteridine Reductase；DHPR）及喋呤甲醇胺脫水酶（Pterin-4α-Carbinolamine Dehydratase；PCD）。依其酶缺乏的不同，會有不同的臨床症狀及診斷方法，其治療方法也不相同。

